location.fullValue: Canvas Plan, Greenways at Sand Creek

data.description: Beautiful updated two story home on top of the hill with incredible mountain views! Low utility costs due to solar panels! Very spacious bedrooms could fit queen sized beds with plenty of additional room!  Conveniently located close to parks, schools, shopping and is and ideal location near Schriever AFB and Peterson Space Force Base. This home features an open concept floor plan, large windows for abundant natural light, and wood flooring! The main level has a huge, bright, welcoming eat-in kitchen with center island and plenty of cabinet storage. Large living room with a fireplace! The upstairs features a laundry area, master/primary bedroom with adjoining updated bathroom! 2 additional well appointed bedrooms and additional full bathroom.  The fully finished basement features a family room, a game/entertainment room, and full bathroom. Home shows the pride of home ownership. Low taxes - not in a special taxing district and no HOA! Don't miss this opportunity to make this house your home!
